<concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.2" id="conref-tasks-concept"><title>conref_tasks_concept</title><shortdesc/><prolog><author translate="no" type="creator">Eamonn Smith &lt;eamonn.smith@puppet.com&gt;</author></prolog><conbody><p>Install a&#160;Puppet Enterprise&#160;agent to  regularly pull configuration catalogs from a&#160;Puppet&#160;master, and apply them
            to your target <ph conkeyref="ProductNames/linux"/> or <ph conkeyref="ProductNames/windows"/> nodes. The agent maintains the node configuration you want.</p><p>Install, upgrade, or uninstall  packages on vulnerable nodes without installing an agent. </p><p>Manage and inspect system  services on vulnerable nodes.</p><p>Execute an arbitrary shell command on vulnerable nodes without installing an agent.</p><p>Upload your scripts to be converted into tasks, or upload a Puppet module containing a task, to help remediate a vulnerability.</p></conbody></concept>